  Thy pity without end?<br />
  O make me Thine for ever;<br />
  And should I fainting be,<br />
  Lord let me never, never<br />
  Outlive my love for Thee.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>(Gerhardt X) Be near me when I‚Äôm dying,<br />
