  Come, Lord, and set me free.<br />
  These eyes new faith receiving,<br />
  From Jesus shall not move;<br />
  For he, who dies believing,<br />
  Dies safely through Thy love.</p>
  </li>
</ol>

<p>Miss Winkworth, 1855, in her <em>Lyra Germanica</em>, 1st Series.</p>

<ol>
